subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Norfolk State failed to become the first No. 15 seed to advance to the Round of 16 as the Gators scored 25 consecutive early points and stopped the Spartans’ feel-good story cold.
